title.rendered: Culinary dining Set Dining Table and Chair

excerpt.rendered:
Elevate your dining experience with the Culinary Dining Set. This meticulously crafted dining table and chair ensemble seamlessly blends style and comfort. The cushioned upholstered dining chairs provide extended comfort, making every meal a delightful occasion. Ideal for both compact spaces and larger dining areas, this set exudes sophistication and practicality. Explore the Culinary Dining Set to transform your dining room into a space of culinary delight.

Features: 

  • Comfortable sitting for 6 people
  • Faux leather upholstery with tufted back

Dimension:

  • Table : 29.4″ H x 35.4″ W x 59.1″ L
  • Chair : 38.0″ H x 17.3″ W x 18.3″ L

“Note: All our products are made to order.”
